title: AshesTo Antarctica.mp3
description:
1 x 45 mins

Re-post of a torrent lost after an HDD failure.

Jill is recently widowed. She knows that her husband had worked in Antarctica many years before and was captivated by the place. She there fore embarks on a cruise of the southern ocean, determined to leave his ashes in the place he loved. Unfortunately, it is not as easy as she imagines.

A comic sub-plot involves Jill's man mad sister's pursuit of the leader of the expedition!

The play comes to a very satisfactory conclusion for Jill - if not her sister!
